Lisimba
=======

- icons for the menu items.

- import rules
- GNU GPL.

- open from http.


Desmond
=======

- Open address book from a file.
- If the file was modified, reload the address book.

- Open address book from database.
- If the database was updated, reload the address book.

- Open address from a web service.
- If the address book was changed, reload the address book.

- Announce the next birthday if less then n days.

- Display a NotifyIcon.

